{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_04_04",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 04 04",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――セミファイナル目前のある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day‚ just before the semifinals",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.16666676203409847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、はあ……もう一回、最初から……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant …One more time‚ from the beginning…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 8.306893444061279
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "（三人が揃って練習できる日は、残り少ないし）\n（一人の時間を有効に使って、仕上げていかないと……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(We don't have many days left to practice together as three‚)\n(so I have to make good use of my time alone and perfect it…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.636513706048328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 17.123560110727947
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 17.123560110727947
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？　話し声？\n……じゃない、歌だ。この曲は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmm? Is that someone talking?\n…No‚ it's singing. This song…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.006893444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 24.940226777394578
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "（社長室から聴こえてくる）\n（これ、サニーピースの曲……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It's coming from the president's office.)\n(Is this… Sunny Peace's song…?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5402267774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 30.240226777394582
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "相手は大胆な戦略変更に出てきましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They've made a bold strategic change.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.240226777394618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "これまでのようにはいかないでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It won't be as easy as before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.973560110727945,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "長瀬麻奈の再来……その肩書きや声を封じて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagase Mana's second coming… by sealing that title and voice‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.40689344406128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "迷いのない、自分達の歌を見つけにいく……か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "they're going to find their own song‚ without hesitation… huh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.8402267774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "彼女達はもう、長瀬麻奈を見ていません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're no longer looking at Nagase Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.40689344406128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "見据えているのは、もっと先の未来です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Their eyes are set on a future far beyond.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1402267774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ですがトリエルやリズノワは違う……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ TRINITYAiLE and LizNoir are different…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.473560110727945,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "彼女達は、長瀬麻奈に囚われています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're captivated by Nagase Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.27356011072796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "彼女を超えなくてはならないという、呪縛に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the curse of having to surpass her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1068934440613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "セミファイナル、それが結果にどう影響するか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The semifinals‚ how will that affect the results…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.0402267774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 69.2402267773946
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 69.2402267773946
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "あの、一ついいですか\n……さくらさんは、もう歌わないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ may I ask one thing?\n…Sakura-san‚ she's not going to sing anymore?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.07356011072794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。まだ直接本人に聞いた訳じゃないけど\nさくらはもう麻奈の声では歌わないと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes. Though I haven't heard it directly from her yet‚\nI don't think Sakura will sing with Mana's voice anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9402267774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 84.90689344406128
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.90689344406128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 86.91671205361683
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今のさくらは\nそれでいいと俺は思っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I think it’s okay\nfor Sakura as she is now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.91671205361683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なぜならさくら……そして琴乃は、麻奈と肩を並べる\n……いや、それ以上になる可能性を秘めているから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because Sakura… and Kotono have the potential to stand shoulder to shoulder with Mana…\n…No‚ to even surpass her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.71671205361685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 103.0500453869502
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 103.0500453869502
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "私は、長瀬麻奈さんをもちろん尊敬してますし\n大好きです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I of course respect Nagase Mana-san‚\nand I love her very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.28337872028352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 109.77376335400803
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それじゃいつまでも自分だけの歌は歌えません\nこのセミファイナルから、自分の声で歌います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if I continue like that‚ I'll never be able to sing my own song.\nI will sing with my own voice from this semifinal onwards.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.00709668734136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 118.64043002067469
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "……だから、麻奈さんに関係する質問は\nやめてもらってもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ could you please refrain from\nasking me any questions related to Mana-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.80709668734129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 124.7573352331
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 124.7573352331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "（確かに、さくらさんの宣言には）\n（何一つ迷いがなくて力強かった……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Indeed‚ Sakura-san's declaration was)\n(powerful and without a shred of doubt…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.10709668734137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 132.13126902519133
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらさんも、ある種、同類だと思ってた）\n（長瀬麻奈の存在に比べられてしまう側として）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I thought Sakura-san was‚ in a way‚ similar to me)\n(as someone who's compared to Nagase Mana's existence.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.9312690252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 139.4646023585246
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 143.5312690251912
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_04-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、もし、もうそんな次元じゃなくなっていたら？）\n（明らかに私よりも、先へ進んでいたとしたら……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But what if she's already beyond that level?)\n(What if she's clearly progressed further than me…?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5312690252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 147.78703501640214
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "長瀬麻奈に囚われているのは事実だろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true that they're captivated by Nagase Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.78703501640214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "しかし言い換えれば、それは明確な目標でもある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But in other words‚ that's also a clear goal for them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.4870350164021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あえてうやむやな物を指針とした彼女達より",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They have a clearer path than those who use vague things as their guiding principles.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.75370168306878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
